  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in the United States of America. The aim of this trial is to
      investigate safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics (the exposure of the trial drug in the
      body) and pharmacodynamics (the effect of the investigated drug on the body) of liraglutide
      in obese children aged 7 to 11 years
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
